snippet.title: 2K Drive Dev Diary 1
snippet.description:
2K and the development team at Lucid, creators of Blur and Project Gotham Racing, are excited to present a behind the scenes first look at their latest project, 2K Drive -- the recently announced, console quality racing game coming soon to iOS.

2K Drive Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/2KDrive
